---

When you have a button or similar element that navigates to a new page, use the `Link` component from Next.js to navigate to the new page. For example:

```tsx
<Link href="/new-page">
  <Button>Go to new page</Button>
</Link>
```

**Avoid using router.push() to navigate to a new page whenever possible.**
